<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>الباب المائة فيما قيل في إِكرام النفس وتَرْك إِهانتها<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٨٣٨)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>.................<span class="c5"> :</span> <span class="c2">(من الطويل)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١ - نَفْسَكَ أَكْرِمْهَا فَإنَّكَ إِنْ تَهُنْ ... عَلَيْكَ فَلَنْ تَلْقَى لَهَا الدَّهْرَ مُكْرِمَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٨٣٩)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ زُهَيْرٌ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - وَمَنْ يَغْتَرِبْ يَحْسِبْ عَدُوًّا صَدِيقَهُ ... وَمَنْ لَمْ يُكَرِّمْ نَفْسَهُ لَمْ يُكَرَّمِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
