<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الْمُرِّيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١ - وَأُكْرِمُ نَفْسِي إِنَّنِي إِنْ أَهَنْتُهَا ... وَجَدِّكَ لَمْ تُكْرَمْ عَلَى أَحَدٍ بَعْدِي<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٨٤١)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ صَالِحُ بنُ عبْدِ الْقُدُّوسِ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>١ - إِذَا مَا أَهَنْتَ النَّفْسَ لَمْ تَلْقَ مُكْرِمًا ... لَهَا بَعْدَمَا عَرَّضْتَهَا لِهَوَانِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
